The paper is about social network analysis (SNA) on online social networks (OSNs), which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI) and social computing (cs.SOC). The paper also discusses sampling algorithms, which are related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper proposes a new approach for crawling and sampling multiple OSNs, which is related to databases (cs.DB).
